parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Grinding noise when turning
loss of power steering
clunking noise in the steering wheel
intermittent pulling surges in the steering wheel
constant corrections
loose feel
and sudden failure of the power steering pump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering gear and rack can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Loud noise when turning
vibration
and shifting to the right
inner tie rod separation from the rack and pinion assembly
and failure of the steering gear and rack.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tie Rod and Ball Joint Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tie rod and ball joint can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Clunking noise in the steering wheel
play in the steering wheel
and failure of the upper ball joints and tie rods.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alarm system can cause the vehicle to be left unsecured, leading to potential theft or damage.
symptoms: Alarm system fails to arm
red light on the dashboard does not flash
and alarm system only works intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock or handle can cause the door to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door does not open from the inside
the door handle breaks or separates
the door lock becomes stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the hood molding can cause the piece to fly off and hit other vehicles or pedestrians, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The hood molding becomes detached while driving
the hood molding flies off and hits another vehicle or pedestrian
the hood molding is not properly secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front end or steering system can cause the vehicle to become unstable, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering is loose or unstable
the vehicle shakes or vibrates while driving
the tie rods or rack and pinion need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trunk lid or strut can cause the trunk lid to fall, potentially causing injury or damage.
symptoms: The trunk lid does not stay up
the trunk lid falls without warning
the struts need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of cosmetic or trim components can cause aesthetic damage and potentially lead to more serious issues.
symptoms: The trim or molding becomes damaged or detached
the windshield is not properly secured
the airbag cover cracks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not provided with the necessary protection.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dashboard Cracking and Airbag Deployment Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard, particularly in the area where the airbags are deployed, can lead to airbag malfunction or failure to deploy, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracking of the dashboard
particularly in the area where the airbags are deployed
airbag deployment failure
and concerns about the safety of the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unwanted airbag deployment can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as well as damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbag deployment while driving
without any apparent reason or crash.
